## Ancho a largo



::: {.cell hash='2-manipulacion_y_limpieza_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-38_42e67f08b6df1aa482252e8a4661e2d1'}

```{.r .cell-code}
colonias_largo <- colonias %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = c(Abarrotes,Supermercado,Minisuper),
    names_to = "tipo_negocio",
    values_to = "n_negocios")
```
